      <p><a href="ch73s35.html#MonstersAnimals128">Porpoises</a> are mammals that tend to be playful, friendly, and helpful. A typical <a href="ch73s35.html#MonstersAnimals128">porpoise</a> is 4 to 6 feet long and weighs 110 to 160 pounds. The statistics presented here can describe any small <a href="ch73s46.html#MonstersAnimals179">whale</a> of similar size.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
